            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Nvim enables syntax by default, which implicitly enables filetype detection (`:h syntax-loading`). To disable filetype detection you need to also disable syntax:\r\n```\r\nsyntax off\r\nfiletype off\r\nfiletype plugin off\r\nfiletype indent off\r\n```",
